  "description": "Ensure Counter Suffix Displays on Same Line as Counter Number\n\nFix the layout of counter components so that the suffix text appears inline with the counter value rather than wrapping to a new line.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify all counter displays in the application where suffix text exists\n- Apply CSS or layout adjustments to prevent line breaks between number and suffix\n- Use appropriate white-space or flexbox properties to keep elements together\n- Test with various counter values (short and long numbers) to ensure consistent behavior\n- Verify responsive behavior across different screen sizes\n- Ensure the fix works with different suffix lengths and content",
